		<td><b>NES Header editor released</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've created a tiny NES Header editor (NESHead). It comes with a GUI (yay! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />) and should be pretty easy to use.
<br />It's in beta-state so use at your own risk. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />Download can be found here:
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.anes.se/FDSExplorer/">http://www.anes.se/FDSExplorer/</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


